Q: At a restaurant, each adult meal costs $5 and kids eat free.
If a group of 15 people came in and 8 were kids,
how much would it cost for the group to eat?

Qt: At a restaurant, each adult meal costs A and kids eat free.
If a group of B people came in and C were kids,
how much would it cost for the group to eat?
Mapping: {A:5, B:15, C:8}

